Promotion rule

The summarizer marks a recipe PROMISING only when:

Mean top-1 change is positive.
Mean MRR change is positive.
At least half the runs improve top-1.
At least half the runs improve MRR.
Top-4 does not decline by more than 0.5 percentage points.

A single lucky seed is not enough.

